room_title: Escape room "Dark Side of the Moon" by Houston Escape Room in Houston
review: We played the Dark Side of the Moon room and had the Agent in Training as our game master. It was a lot of fun, they had creative puzzles and clever clues! I work at an escape room in Nashville and these guys know how it's done! A lot of fun and would recommend to anyone new or experienced!

room_title: Escape room "Dark Side of the Moon" by Houston Escape Room in Houston
review: Went my birthday, and it was so much fun! This is my third room. Most of our team, of 10, were first timers, not knowing what to expect and they enjoyed it. We escaped it with 3 minutes and 12 seconds left. The staff is pretty chill and laid back.

room_title: Escape room "Dark Side of the Moon" by Houston Escape Room in Houston
review: Went with my company and it was a blast! We worked together and made it out with less then a minute remaining. The staff were FANTASTIC. The girl in our room was professional, calm and seemed to enjoy us running around like maniacs! I would do it again in a heartbeat!
